Nigerian Government has cleared backlog payment of 8,900 NPower Batches A and B beneficiaries. The Npower also informed Nigerians to apply for ‘Next level of empowerment’ in order to be eligible for N30,000. This information was confirmed in a post shared Wednesday morning via their official Twitter handle. The statement read, “BACKLOGS PAYMENT! 8,900 N-POWER BATCHES A and B BENEFICIARIES have been cleared for payment of their five months arrears of their STIPENDS as the SMS has been sent to the eligible ones. “You’re to join others, login to https://nexit-fmhds.cbn.gov.ng/auth/login for the next level of empowerment”. The beneficiaries of Npower scheme enjoy N30, 000 monthly stipend monthly for services offered.